<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pip on Margrop Blog</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/tag/pip/</link><description>Recent content in Pip on Margrop Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 16 Jun 2021 11:13:46 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.margrop.net/en/tag/pip/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Issue where pip becomes unusable after pip install --upgrade pip on CentOS 7: ImportError: No module named typing</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-no-module-named-typing-after-upgrade-pip/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Jun 2021 11:13:46 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-no-module-named-typing-after-upgrade-pip/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="problem-description"&gt;Problem Description&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;pip安装某第三方 SDK，提示升级 pip，按提示升级 pip 后报错&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="pip-upgrade-command-that-causes-the-error"&gt;pip Upgrade Command that Causes the Error&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;pip install --upgrade pip
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="pip-error-message"&gt;pip Error Message&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Traceback &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;most recent call last&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; File &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/bin/pip&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, line 9, in &amp;lt;module&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; load_entry_point&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;pip==21.1.2&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;console_scripts&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;pip&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; File &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/pkg_resources.py&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, line 378, in load_entry_point
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; get_distribution&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;dist&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.load_entry_point&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;group, name&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; File &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/pkg_resources.py&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, line 2566, in load_entry_point
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; ep.load&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; File &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/pkg_resources.py&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, line 2260, in load
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; entry &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; __import__&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;self.module_name, globals&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;,globals&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;__name__&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;])&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; File &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;/usr/lib/python2.7/site-packages/pip/__init__.py&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, line 1, in &amp;lt;module&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; from typing import List, Optional
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ImportError: No module named typing
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>